=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_Latch_ex1 ===

DESCRIPTION: A dark clean sound, with fm_or_inharmonic oscillator character around 414 Hz, featuring punchy attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, and filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: dark
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: clean
  spectral_complexity_mean: moderate
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 414.1060
  harmonic_decay_rate: -4.1539
  harmonic_regularity: 0.8871
  pitch_clarity: 24.3350
  inharmonicity: 0.3792
  type: fm_or_inharmonic
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -21.2854
  resonance_freq: 581.3965

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Latch Example 1
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/Latch.html
// Tags: Latch, Classes
// ---
// --- Example 1 ---
{ Blip.ar(Latch.ar(WhiteNoise.ar, Impulse.ar(9)) * 400 + 500, 4, 0.2) }.play;
